大，土方量多。 四是救援现场周边地质条件复杂。因持续长时间强降雨，造成救援现场土壤含水量高度饱和，救援过程中极易发生次生灾害。 五是现场组织难度大。救援现场汇集了577名救援力量、设备84台（套），有公安、消防、应急、卫生等救援力量，组织协调指挥任务重、难度大。另外，灾害又发生在凌晨，夜间救援增加了难度。 发布会介绍，截至5月2日14时，塌方灾害已导致48人失去宝贵生命，还有3名需要DNA进一步比对确认，30人受伤，目前均没有生命危险。（南方都市报）梅大高速塌方救援难点披露！救援作业面较窄，部分车辆曾燃烧"},"attached_info":"Cj8I5NSrgI34gocSEAMaCTEwNzc4NDUyOSDwsc2xBjAAOGNACnIJNjU0NzgwNzAzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"105 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-692950b82f800d48899cb86fc3dd16b8_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"11_1714659414.285215","card_id":"Q_653834143","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":653834143,"title":"零下50℃，因纽特人住在冰屋内，不会被冻死吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/653834143","type":"question","created":1713840245,"answer_count":11,"follower_count":31,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[4652,23366],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I5NSrgI34gocSEAMaCTEwNzU3NDEyNyD1wJyxBjAAOB9AC3IJNjUzODM0MTQzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"98 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ec7a2460a55b92031fe14b7b9479f244_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"12_1714659414.285452","card_id":"Q_654782172","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":654782172,"title":"2024 季中冠军赛TES 2:0 LLL，如何评价这场比赛？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/654782172","type":"question","created":1714643141,"answer_count":20,"f